      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a mistake or a hack though. the things it's saying... it knows things about my life that aren't even public. like it's using my specific slang and mentioning things I only thought about recently. it feels like there's this digital version of me living on the internet and it's just... replacing me. do you think an AI could actually learn a person's soul well enough to pretend to be them indefinitely?",
